UNKNOWN-LINK-LSA-TYPE - Retrieve

GET Cisco-IOS-XR-ipv6-ospfv3-oper:ospfv3/processes/process/{process-name}/vrfs/vrf/{vrf-name}/database-table/lsa-internal-table/lsa/lsa-info/unknown-link-lsa-type/

Retrieve operation of resource: unknown-link-lsa-type

process-name: string
in path

ID of process-name

vrf-name: string
in path

ID of vrf-name

200 OK
unknown-link-lsa-type_schema

Successful operation

400 Bad Request

Internal Error

Response Content-Types: application/json
Response Example (200 OK) 
{
  
"unknown-link-lsa-type": { Unknown Link Scope LSA

    
"interface-name": "string", LSA interface name 

    
"lsa-header": { Header information 

      
"lsa-type": "integer", LSA type

      
"sequence-number": "integer", Current Sequence number

      
"lsa-age": "integer", LSA's Age (s)

      
"checksum": "integer", Checksum value

      
"is-do-not-age-lsa": "boolean", If true, Do Not Age this LSA

      
"advertising-router": "string", Router ID of Advertising Router

      
"ls-id": "integer", LS ID

      
"is-graceful-restart-active": "boolean", If true, if grace restart is active 

      
"lsa-area-id": "string" Area ID in decimal or dotted-decimal format

    },
    
"is-sham-link": "boolean", If true, it is a sham link 

    
"lsa-detail": { Detailed LSA information

      
"is-flood-pending": "boolean", If true, the reason not to delete this LSA is\nbecause waiting for flooding or retransmission

      
"minute-table-index": "integer", Minute table index

      
"is-advertising-router-reachable": "boolean", If true, Advertising Router is reachable

      
"nsr-flood-required": "boolean", If true, the reason not to delete this LSA is\nbecause it is pending flooding on switchover

      
"is-acknowledged": "boolean", If true, the reason not to delete this LSA is\nbecause it's Acknowledgement list is not empty 

      
"lsa-flood-required-post-fail-over": "boolean", LSA flood required after FO

      
"is-deleted": "boolean", If true, flag is set to delete this LSA 

      
"second-table-index": "integer", Second table index

      
"is-partial-spf": "boolean", If true, the reason not to delete this LSA is\nbecause it is in partial SPF queue

      
"lsa-length": "integer", Length of the LSA

      
"is-no-delete": "boolean", If true, the reason not to delete this LSA is\nbecause delete flag not set on this LSA

      
"rate-limit": "boolean", If true, the reason not to delete this LSA is\nbecause waiting for next wait-interval to expire

      
"is-routing-table": "boolean", If true, the reason  not to delete this LSA is\nbecause it has a contributing entry in the\nrouting table 

      
"is-neighbor-exchange": "boolean", If true, the reason  not to delete this LSA is\nbecause neighbor is in exchange state

      
"free-time": "integer", The amount of time since the last check was made\nto free this LSA (s)

      
"is-maximum-aged": "boolean", If true, the reason not to delete this LSA is\nbecause it is in Maxage Queue

      
"lsa-sync-state": "string", State of LSA sync with active

      
"is-nsr-ack-pending": "boolean", If true, the reason not to delete this LSA is\nbecause NSR ACK from standby is pending

      
"is-routing-bit": "boolean" If true, Routing Bit set on the LSA

    },
    
"virtual-link-id": "integer", Virtual link ID 

    
"is-virtual-link": "boolean", If true, it is a virtual link 

    
"sham-link-id": "integer" Shamlink ID 

  }
}

LSA-TABLE - Retrieve

GET Cisco-IOS-XR-ipv6-ospfv3-oper:ospfv3/processes/process/{process-name}/vrfs/vrf/{vrf-name}/areas/area/{area-id}/database-table/lsa-table/

Retrieve operation of resource: lsa-table

process-name: string
in path

ID of process-name

vrf-name: string
in path

ID of vrf-name

area-id: string
in path

ID of area-id

200 OK
lsa-table_schema

Successful operation

400 Bad Request

Internal Error

Response Content-Types: application/json
